results.title: [Tokolysis and dose-dependent effects of beta-blocking with atenolol in the rabbit].
results.text_hl: By application of @CHEMICAL_Fenoterol @CHEMICAL_MESH:D005280 @@@Fenoterol@@@ (0.01 mg/min) we had complete @<m>DISEASE_Labor_Pain</m> @DISEASE_MESH:D048949 @@@labor@@@ inhibition (P). Increasing dosages of @<m>CHEMICAL_Atenolol</m> @CHEMICAL_MESH:D001262 @@@Atenolol@@@ (T1 = 0.05 mg/min, T2 = 0.10 mg/min, T3 = 0.25 mg/min) followed.
